---
title: Learning Textografo Benchmark
---

@theme clean
@direction TB
@layout grid

#start Sign-up
Go through Tutorial

#decision Tutorial Done?
  -> yes: Create Flowcharts
  -> "No - Let's go step by step": Create a new flowchart

Create Flowcharts

#decision All Fine?
  -> yes: #circle Congrats! Level 1
  -> "No - Check This": Create a new flowchart

#circle Congrats! Level 1

#decision Ready for next level?
  -> yes: Create a cross-functional flowchart
  -> No: Click on the PLAY to check your work

Create a cross-functional flowchart
Create a subprocess
Create a bridge
Connect Distant Shape

#decision Done?
  -> yes: Click on PLAY to check your work
  ~> no: Create a cross-functional flowchart

Click on PLAY to check your work
#circle Congrats! Level 2
#end "You're done...for the moment :)"

// The "No" branch from "Tutorial Done?" or "All Fine?"
Create a new flowchart
Create a decision bridge
Add a label to a connector
Zoom on a particular part of diagram

#decision Done?
  -> yes: #circle Congrats! Level 1
  ~> no: Create a new flowchart

// Exit path for "No" on "Ready for next level?"
Click on the PLAY to check your work
#end "Have a rest and come back later! :)"
